<p class="small-margin-before">The exclusive autographed Head tennis racket and a white Le Coq Sportif T-shirt from Cedric Pioline, pro tennis player, former No. 4 in ATP ranking.<br>Throughout his career, he reached the men's singles final at the 1993 US Open and at Wimbledon in 1997 and won Davis Cups in 1996 and 2001. He also won 5 ATP tournaments in singles. Currently, Mr. Pioline is the Co-Captain and coach of French national team.<br>In 2017 Cedric Pioline joined TokenStars as the sports ambassador.</p>
